ygData.messageBody:
first off, I've been on this mailing list for a long time, since issue 7 or
so. NOTHING on tis list is BS, so don't say it is. second thing. on a
website, EQ trading corner, I looked up matriels for tinkering, and it said
fishing pole, sold on two vendors.Was the person too lazy to write all the
places where you could find fishing poles, or do they know something we
don't? The vendors were someone on Kerra island/wisp island, in eruds
crossing i think, and someone with a ogrelike name in Lake Rathe or Rathe
Mountains(can't remember which). this is all speculating though. Last thing,
right now I'm on aol(blagh) and I want to change to something else.Any ideas
on what I should get?
